description:
ON Today's episode of the Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses the #1 seeded Bucks getting knocked out of the playoffst. Will Giannis be in Milwaukee for the long run? There's a player that DP thinks could get them over the hump. Pro Football Focus' George Chahrouri and NBA HOF Reggie Miller both join the program. Plus, who's your favorite 90's band of all time. The guys share theirs.
